In the following the instructions used to generate the lessons for different languages.
Where multiple commands are present, the lessons have then been combined manually.

## Italian

python ../ktouch-lesson-generator.py --lesson-title-prefix=Lezione ../lessons/italian.txt ../dictionaries/dict-it.txt
python ../ktouch-lesson-generator.py --lesson-title-prefix=Lezione --max-word-length=7 ../lessons/italian_symbols.txt ../dictionaries/dict-it.txt
python ../ktouch-lesson-generator.py --lesson-title-prefix=Lezione --max-word-length=7 ../lessons/italian_numbers.txt ../dictionaries/dict-it.txt

## Extended symbols

python ../ktouch-lesson-generator.py  --max-word-length=7 ../lessons/symbols_extended.txt ../dictionaries/dict-en_uk.txt
